OL,3,CHow Scappaticci revealed inner
OL,4,Cworkings of IRA's 'nutting squad'
OL,6,F"They think they're going to go
OL,7,Fhome...but they don't."
OL,9,F10 words that sum up the Provisional
OL,10,FIRA's internal security unit.
OL,12,FThat sentence was spoken by the person
OL,13,Fwho knew exactly how the feared
OL,14,Fnutting squad operated.
OL,16,FWhen he spoke to reporters from ITV's
OL,17,FCook Report in the 1990s he didn't
OL,18,Fcall himself Freddie or Stakeknife,
OL,19,Fbut that is exactly who he was.
