OL,3,CHow Scappaticci revealed inner
OL,4,Cworkings of IRA's 'nutting squad'
OL,6,FScappaticci broke ranks to speak to
OL,7,Fthe current affairs program after it
OL,8,Fhad aired allegations around Martin
OL,9,FMcGuinness a few days earlier.
OL,11,FThe reporters focused on what he had
OL,12,Fto say about the Sinn Fein rather than
OL,13,Fthe internal workings of the internal
OL,14,Fsecurity unit, but we did get a
OL,15,Fglimpse into how the unit operated.
OL,17,F"Standard procedure is to strip them
OL,18,Fand debug them, just to see if they
OL,19,Fare wired up and then they usually put
OL,20,Fa boiler suit on them."
