OL,3,CHow Scappaticci revealed inner
OL,4,Cworkings of IRA's 'nutting squad'
OL,6,F"They then get you into a room,
OL,7,Fblindfold you, strip you."
OL,9,F"The room is cold, they make you all
OL,10,Fsorts of promises, everyone is at
OL,11,Fbreaking point"
OL,13,F"They think they are going to go home
OL,14,Fbut they don't."
OL,16,FThis was coming from the man who was
OL,17,Ftasked with being a spy catcher for
OL,18,Fthe IRA while himself being the chief
OL,19,Fspy among his comrades.
