OL,6,FLittle did they know when he carried
OL,7,Fcoffins, stood shoulder to shoulder
OL,8,Fwith them that he was an informer
OL,9,Fbeing paid #80K a year for his
OL,10,Fservices.
OL,12,FThe significance of his role can't be
OL,13,Funder estimated and while there are
OL,14,Fquestions about how many lives he
OL,15,Fsaved the knowledge he would have
OL,16,Fpossessed can't be underestimated.
