OL,3,CHow Scappaticci revealed inner
OL,4,Cworkings of IRA's 'nutting squad'
OL,6,FRichard O'Rawe, author of Stakeknife's
OL,7,FDirty War, told UTV: "As head of
OL,8,Finternal security unit, all major
OL,9,Foperations in the Belfast had to go
OL,10,Fthrough him beforehand.
OL,12,F"He was actually in many ways running
OL,13,FBelfast"
OL,15,F"If he was running Belfast the British
OL,16,Fforces were running Belfast."
OL,18,FA lot of effort went into protecting
OL,19,FStakeknife, people lost their lives so
OL,20,Fhis cover could remain intact.
