OL,3,CHow Scappaticci revealed inner
OL,4,Cworkings of IRA's 'nutting squad'
OL,6,FDecisions were taken by people within
OL,7,Fthe intelligence services on who
OL,8,Fshould live and who should die.
OL,10,FSome would have been other agents and
OL,11,Fothers would have been innocent people
OL,12,Faccused of being an informer.
OL,14,FBrian Rowan, security correspondent,
OL,15,Fsaid: "This was one Army agent
OL,16,Finterrogating other army agents.
OL,18,F"In all the grotesqueness of that
OL,19,Fdirty war, the Army had someone in the
OL,20,Fmiddle of this."
