OL,3,CHow Scappaticci revealed inner
OL,4,Cworkings of IRA's 'nutting squad'
OL,6,F"Not tied to the chair, not pleading
OL,7,Ffor mercy, not speaking his last
OL,8,Fwords, but running the show."
OL,10,FDespite being outed in 2003 and then
OL,11,Fgoing on the run Freddie Scappaticci
OL,12,Falways denied he was Stakeknife.
OL,14,FThere were few who fully believed him,
OL,15,Fbut unlike other informers the IRA
OL,16,Fnever tortured and murdered him.
OL,18,FBrian Rowan said "There was his
OL,19,Fpredicament, and there was their
OL,20,Fpredicament.
